title: 707. Super Bowl Contenders Draft
itunes:title: 707. Super Bowl Contenders Draft
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks are back with a new episode of Move the Sticks. On this special show, the guys start by reacting to the Jacksonville Jaguars and New Orleans Saints game, with a focus on Jaguars quarterback Trevor Lawrence and the Saints defense. Next, the pair do a breakdown of the first-round rookie quarterbacks after Preseason Week 2. To wrap up the show, the duo pick their top 10 Super Bowl contenders by doing a 1-10 draft.


Move the Sticks is a part of the NFL Podcasts Network.
